diff --git a/04_SOFTWARE/p31ca/DEPLOY.md b/04_SOFTWARE/p31ca/DEPLOY.md
index 7e60d08..effb89b 100644
--- a/04_SOFTWARE/p31ca/DEPLOY.md
+++ b/04_SOFTWARE/p31ca/DEPLOY.md
@@ -7,6 +7,8 @@
 | **`p31ca`** | `04_SOFTWARE/p31ca/` | `p31ca.org`, `www.p31ca.org` |
 | **`p31-hearing-ops`** | `04_SOFTWARE/p31-hearing-ops/` | `ops.p31ca.org` only |
 
+**Passport + deploy** — from `04_SOFTWARE/p31ca/`: `npm run deploy` runs `predeploy` → `passport:verify` (and build). Full P31 home: sync authoring first with `npm run sync:passport` at workspace root, or `npm run passport:sync` from `p31ca/`. Stale `public/passport-generator.html` fails the deploy. **Wrangler** is pinned in `package.json` (pages deploy: `project-name p31ca`).
+
 Deploying **any other app’s `dist/`** to project **`p31ca`** replaces the hub for **every** domain on that project.
 
 ## Recover if the apex shows Hearing Ops (or any wrong app)
